msgid "Upgrading From 1.x to 2.x"
msgstr "1.x から 2.x へのアップグレード"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Driver version 2 dropped some static configuration options in favour of "
"managing these options at runtime using <<s-openstack-volume-types,volume "
"types>>."
msgstr ""
"ドライバーバージョン 2 は、実行時に <<s-openstack-volume-types,ボリュームタイ"
